<About title="General Information">
  <p>
    The Tech is the student newspaper of the Massachusetts Institute of
    Technology, published since 1881. It is one of the oldest and largest
    student newspapers in the country, written, edited, and produced entirely
    by students.
  </p>
  <p>
    The Tech is published in print and online, covering campus news, opinion,
    arts, sports, and the broader MIT community. The newspaper is editorially
    independent and operated as a non-profit.
  </p>
</About>
